reviewText: So cute! The Old school cuteness of cartoons from years ago.  The "bad guys" are not scary but silly and whole thing is just cute, cute, cute!

I gave this a 5 even though I haven't seen this movie in 15 years. I was young and remember picking out this movie all the time at the white video store down the block. Amazing the stuff you remember and find on the internet. I had loved this movie and so had my sibs so it must of been awesome
